This repo is the template for the per-account bootstrap stack — it provisions
the foundational AWS resources every Devotica project repo needs in order to
operate: state bucket, lock table, KMS key, OIDC provider, IAM role, audit
trail.

Each AWS account gets its own *instance* repo generated from this template
(e.g. devotica-labs/devotica-sandbox-bootstrap, clientA/terraform-bootstrap).
The template repo contains code only — no state, no account-specific data.

